---
// About section with bio and featured recording
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-[#2a2a2a]">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-[#f5f5f0] mb-12 text-center">
      About Nilo
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Bio Content -->
      <div class="space-y-6 text-[#a0a0a0] text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#009739] rounded-full mt-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-[#f5f5f0]">20+ years playing professionally</strong> — performing, recording, and teaching across multiple continents, bringing authentic Brazilian musical traditions to students worldwide.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#fedd00] rounded-full mt-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-[#f5f5f0]">Musical heritage</strong> — Son of a renowned studio musician, growing up immersed in the craft of composition, arrangement, and the subtleties of tone and timing.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#002776] rounded-full mt-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-[#f5f5f0]">Spiritual lineage</strong> — Raised within a family deeply connected to the Santo Daime tradition within the Umbanda spiritual practice, bringing a unique perspective on music as a bridge between the material and the sacred.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#009739] rounded-full mt-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-[#f5f5f0]">Teaching approach</strong> — Focused on rhythm, harmony, deep listening, and presence. Music is not just technical skill—it's about connection, intention, and finding your own voice within the tradition.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Featured Recording Card -->
      <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[#3a3a3a] shadow-xl">
        <div class="aspect-square rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-6 max-w-[75%] mx-auto">
          <img 
            src="/niloimg.jpg" 
            alt="Nilo Maia" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#f5f5f0] mb-2">
          Featured Recording
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[#a0a0a0] mb-4">
          Estrela D'Água — recorded at Nova Mídia Studio.
        </p>
        <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-[#3a3a3a]">
          <iframe 
            title="SoundCloud player: Estrela D'Água"
            width="100%"
            height="166"
            scrolling="no"
            frameborder="no"
            allow="autoplay"
            src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//soundcloud.com/nova-midia-studio/estrela-dagua&color=%23009739&auto_play=false&hide_related=false&show_comments=true&show_user=true&show_reposts=false&show_teaser=true"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3 text-right">
          <a 
            href="https://soundcloud.com/nova-midia-studio/estrela-dagua?si=b48bdfd95a534bb193060d4d3386f17e&utm_source=clipboard&utm_medium=text&utm_campaign=social_sharing" 
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-sm text-[#009739] hover:text-[#fedd00] transition-colors"
          >
            Open on SoundCloud ↗
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
